<h3>General Submissions</h3>
<p>If you have suggestions, ideas, or submissions for News &amp; Notes, please send them to <a href="mailto:newsdesk@byui.edu?subject=News and Notes Submission">newsdesk@byui.edu</a>.</p>
<h3>Submitting Items For Sale</h3>
<p><span style="font-size: small;"></span>Employees, retirees, and their spouses may submit items for sale in News &amp; Notes. Submissions must be 35 words or less and should be sent to <a href="mailto:newsdesk@byui.edu?subject=News and Notes Sale Listing">newsdesk@byui.edu</a>.</p>
